Allows an application to write to the SD card.
Allows an application to create network sockets.
Allows an application to connect to and disconnect from Wi-Fi access points and to make changes to configured Wi-Fi networks.

permissions.description: Allows an application to read from the system's various log files. This allows it to discover general information about what you are doing with the phone, potentially including personal or private information.
permissions.name: android.permission.READ_LOGS

permissions.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.
permissions.name: android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE

permissions.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.
permissions.name: android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE

permissions.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.
permissions.name: android.permission.INTERNET

permissions.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.
permissions.name: android.permission.VIBRATE

permissions.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.
permissions.name: android.permission.WAKE_LOCK

permissions.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.
permissions.name: android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE

permissions.description: Allows an application to connect to and disconnect from Wi-Fi access points and to make changes to configured Wi-Fi networks.
permissions.name: android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE

permissions.description: Allows an application to change the state of network connectivity.
permissions.name: android.permission.CHANGE_NETWORK_STATE

permissions.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.
permissions.name: android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE

permissions.description: Allows application to modify global audio settings, such as volume and routing.
permissions.name: android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS
